1.Art and Craft Marketplace:

Problem: Independent artists and crafters often have difficulty reaching a wide audience.
Solution: An app that allows artists and crafters to sell their work, connect with buyers, and promote their products. It can include features like customizable storefronts, payment processing, and marketing tools.

2.Real-Time Traffic and Navigation:

Problem: Traffic congestion and road closures can cause delays and frustration for drivers.
Solution: An app that provides real-time traffic updates, alternative route suggestions, and navigation assistance. It can include features like incident reports, speed trap alerts, and integration with local traffic authorities.
